title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 Day' game

maintext:
ALBUQUERQUE, N.M. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday afternoon’s drawing of the New Mexico Lottery’s “Pick 4 Day” game were:
8-4-9-1
(eight, four, nine, one)
